INTERNAZIONALI BNL D'ITALIA
May 13, 2019
Lorenzo Sonego
START_OF_INTERVIEW_TEXT
 
 
  
 
  
  
   
 
K. KHACHANOV/L. Sonego   
6-3, 6-7, 6-3   
THE MODERATOR: Questions, please.   
 Q.  It's been a very good time for Italian men in tennis right now.  What do you think is causing this current positive time for Italian men in tennis?  
LORENZO SONEGO: (Through translation.)  Yes, it's a very positive moment for Italian tennis, indeed.  It's growing a lot.  We are helping and pushing each other.  Berrettini, Cecchinato, Fognini helps of course the others to follow them and go in the same direction.   
That's what I'm trying right now, to follow their good examples.   
  
  
  
  
  

END_OF_INTERVIEW_TEXT